{"tid":622554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐英年：不用聽戴耀廷解釋　參加論壇已「講出一切 」","createTime":"2018-04-09T08:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T12:22:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a05d2ace07efa517e4078f53bcbcc9fb1fe5e0c5","tid":622554,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180409/s00001/9ebc8bb6d183c2c09a650d8951d02f6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180409%2Fs00001%2F9ebc8bb6d183c2c09a650d8951d02f6d.jpg&h=eeddc76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大法律系副教授戴耀廷在台灣論壇提及「人民自決權利」等言論，遭港府、中央部門和建制派大事批評。戴耀廷事後多次澄清自己不贊成「港獨」，惟全國政協常委、前政務司長唐英年指，「不用聽任何解釋」，認為對方參與有關論壇「已經說明一切」。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年今年晤傳媒時表示，戴耀廷在台灣出席由鼓吹台獨組織舉辦的活動，「意識一句已經講晒」，故不應該容忍這些言論。他又說，「不用聽（戴耀廷）任何解釋」，重申有關論壇由鼓吹台獨組織舉辦，「參加呢個活動，無論講咩都好，已經講出咗一切，所以唔使再去聽佢解釋」，形容戴耀廷解釋只是「花言巧語」。<br />\n<br />\n唐英年強調，香港是國家不可分裂一部分，既是《憲法》，也是「一國兩制」基本原則，不容任何挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180409/s00001/1523261716249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180409%2Fs00001%2F1523261716249&d=sj%2Bd%2B6mvMlltIgHifkvVM%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3cf905d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180409%2Fs00001%2F1523261716249&h=b19d1dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180409/s00001/1523261716249</a>"},{"pid":"baa096b6fba95307ceca7747fb7706ce04dc795b","tid":622554,"uid":77196,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"你僭建果陣都搵你老婆食死貓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683974076fde5460dc8c3d247906d20bb58473f9","tid":622554,"uid":94828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:41:52.000Z","msg"